dataIdInfo.idPurp: This toolset contains several tools to calculate various attributes for each bathymetric high or low feature. These attributes can be used to describe the characteristics of each feature. They can also be used to classify or assign each feature into a feature type based on a morphometric classification scheme.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
The toolset contains the following four tools. Please see the detailed metadata associated with each tool.

  1. Add Shape Attributes High Tool Fast: This tool offers multiprocessing capability and thus is more efficient in generating shape attributes for each bathymetric high feature.

  2. Add Shape Attributes Low Too Fast: This tool offers multiprocessing capability and thus is more efficient in generating shape attributes for each bathymetric low feature.

  3. Add Profile Attributes High Tool Fast: This tool offers multiprocessing capability and thus is more efficient in generating profile attributes for each bathymetric high feature.

  4. Add Profile Attributes Low Tool Fast: This tool offers multiprocessing capability and thus is more efficient in generating profile attributes for each bathymetric low feature.

searchKeys.keyword: This toolset contains several tools to calculate various attributes for each bathymetric high or low feature using multiprocessing capabilities.
